Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是宇宙杀手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are cosmic killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是恒星的末路 它们是恒星的终结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're the end of stars. They're the deaths of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壮观的恒星爆发…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Spectacular stellar detonations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亮度达到了太阳的千亿倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A hundred billion times as bright as the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间照亮了整个星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}...that for an instant outshine a whole galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸以来宇宙中最大 最具活力的事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The most massive, energetic event in the universe...since the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个非同小可的宇宙灾难带来了宇宙万物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Out of this exceptional cosmic catastrophe comes creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 有一个出现在附近 地球生命将告终结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if one struck near here, life on Earth would cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙犯罪一幕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe, the cosmic crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最暴戾神秘的罪魁祸首:\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for a most violent and mysterious force:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Supernovas.
