Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第九集 超新星\N[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 09of19 Supernovas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星 恒星耸人听闻无与伦比的死亡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Supernovas, the sensational and exceptional death of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造了宇宙间最大的爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}produce the biggest blasts in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 只有极少数恒星爆发了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, only a small minority of stars actually explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它们就是轰的一下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but those that do just go ka-blam...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己炸个粉身碎骨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}blowing themselves to smithereens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放的能量超过了太阳一辈子释放的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Releasing more energy than the Sun does in its entire lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达10亿倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by more than a billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壮观的爆炸把大量的致命射线射到宇宙中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The spectacular detonation blasts...vast amounts of lethal radiation into the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果行星系中央的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf a star at the center of a planetary system...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成超新星爆炸的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would go supernova and explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就会彻底消灭那个行星系里所有的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it would probably wipe out all forms of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辐射基本上会将这个行星系的所有行星上的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Radiation would basically sterilize all forms of life...in that planetary system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有生命统统杀死的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on any planet in the planetary system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像刑事侦探研判宇宙犯罪的线索那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like homicide detectives poring over clues to a cosmic crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家用上了现代技术手段\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}scientists use state-of-the-art tools...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即望远镜科技手段来寻找超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}telescopes, and technology to find supernovas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破解它们的产生之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and to solve the mystery of how and why they occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爆发使之成为有趣之事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's an interesting thing because the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事件已经发生了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the event, has already taken place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用望远镜来搜集后我们获得这些线索\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then we get these clues, which we gatherwith our telescopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图弄明白究竟是怎么回事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and try to figure out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为恒星调查员知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As the stellar investigators know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星具有双重星格\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}supernovas have a dual personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们具有绝对的破坏力 同时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They have absolute power to destroy, and, at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们又基本上在创造自我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they are fundamental to creation itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星灭亡之时 爆炸会产生大量的光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When a supernova goes off, the explosion produces a lot of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它也将轻元素变成重元素\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it also produces heavy elements out of the light ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这比如铁 钙或钠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, for example, iron or calcium or sodium...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有元素周期表上的各种元素\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or any of the elements of the periodic table...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西都是来自爆发的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}those things came from exploding stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在太阳形成前就已经消失了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that went off before the Sun was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元素产生于这些巨大的恒星爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The elements produced in these enormous stellar explosions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终造出了行星 植物和人类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}actually make planets, plants, and people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你体内的钙 你呼吸的氧气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The calcium in your bones and the oxygen that you beathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是恒星烹制出来并抛进太空的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}were all cooked up in stars and blown out into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆发恒星的冲击波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The shockwaves from exploding stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会压缩周围的气体云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can compress nearby clouds of gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触发其引力塌缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and trigger their gravitational collapse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果它们开始新的一轮进程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that they begin the renewed process offormation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成新的恒星 行星最后形成生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of new stars, planets, and, ultimately, life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于间接的宇宙旁证的采集\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks to circumstantial cosmic evidence collected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专家估计宇宙间的超新星的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}experts estimate that a mighty supernova goes off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许每一秒钟都会发生一次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}somewhere in the universe once every single second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这是每年大概3000万次的事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So that's something like thirty million peryear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近100亿年左右一直存在于宇宙中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's been going on for the last ten billion years or so...of the universe's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们感觉到宇宙有多大的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Giving us a sense of how big the universe is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如银河系这样的典型星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a typical galaxy like our Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星的突然爆发每百年才一到两回\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a supernova suddenly occurs only once or twice a century.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过谁都不知道下一次什么时候出现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, nobody knows when the next one might come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这完全是个随机事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a completely random process...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我们对下一次出现的时间一无所知\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so we have no idea when the next one will occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能在明天也有可能在5分钟之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be tomorrow, it could be five minutes ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能再要等上一百年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could be another hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果离我们很近的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf it is very close...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会在空中看到非常明亮的事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you would see a very bright event in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它甚至会亮过金星等行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be even brighter than Venus or the planets...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至月球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or even the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可能超过太阳 只要它够亮的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or maybe even the Sun if it's bright enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果超新星和你非常靠近那小命儿肯定完了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf a supernova is too close to you, it can definitely destroy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光会破坏大气层 燃起大火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The flash disrupts the atmosphere, burns things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文学家连续不断地监视天空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronomers are constantly policing the skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对银河系里至少两颗恒星保持着警惕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}keeping a wary eye on at least two stars in the Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们有可能发生悲惨的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that have the potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影响到地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to catastrophically explode close to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个威胁就在于船底座伊塔星中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One that threatens to blow lies in the heart of the Eta Carinae Nebula...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约9000光年外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about 9,000 light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊塔星是我们掌握的一颗超大质量恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eta Carinae is one that we know about...which is a very massive star...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其质量甚至达到了太阳的百倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}maybe even a hundred times the mass of the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命周期很短\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has a very short life...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能其生命很快就将结束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it could be that the end of that life...will take place sometime very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一颗在变成超新星的危险之星是参宿四\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another star in danger of going supernova is Betelgeuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎户座里的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a star in the Orion constellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗炙热的恒星的个头是太阳的15倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This seething star is fifteen times the size of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它比伊塔星更靠近地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This one is even closer than Eta Carinae to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约在500光年外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's roughly 500 light-years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将是一个绚丽的景象甚至在白天都能看到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt'll be a spectacularly brilliant sight, visible even in the daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问参宿四将会爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no question Betelgeuse is going to blow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能就今晚而我们概不知晓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be tonight, for all our ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能在今后的一万年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt could be 10,000 years from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文时间上很短的尺度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}short on an astronomical time scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有可能就今晚 如果我们对此一无所知的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it could be tonight if we're sufficiently ignorant about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 每晚都值得关注它是否已经爆发了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it is worth looking at every night to see whether it's blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的超新星爆发不仅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not only do the massive supernova explosions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造与毁灭了恒星 行星和人类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}create and destroy stars, planets, and people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇士还以宇宙射线的形式释放出强大的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they also unleash powerful energy in the form of cosmic rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些高能带电粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These highly energetic charged particles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在攻击我们地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}strike our planet each and every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有甚者它们具有改变进化的能力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's more, they have the capacity to alter evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们生活在我称之为一个不安定的星系生态中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We live in what l call a disturbed galactic ecology.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个异常火爆活跃的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is a very eruptive, energetic galaxy out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的星球一直遭遇到那种东西的连续攻击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and our planet is going to get pummeled by that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专家称它们会改变我们所了解的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Experts say they can and do change life as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们知道基因突变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, we know that there are genetic mutations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就发生在宇宙射线轰击生命体时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that take place when cosmic rays hit living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它干扰了DNA内部的细胞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt disrupts the DNA inside cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果超新星就在附近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if there were a supernova nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有大量的宇宙射线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there could be a lot more cosmic rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会超过我们平时成百上千甚至百万倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like a hundred or a thousand or a million times more...than we ordinarily get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是古老的物种就有可能导致灭绝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lfyou're the old species, it might lead to your demise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有可能导致新的物种的诞生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it also might lead to new species being developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此超新星可能是变化的媒介\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So a supernova could be an agent of change...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难说其结果如何\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it could be for better or forworse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解了超新星具有创造改变生命的力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Knowing that supernovas have the power...to create and alter life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当务之急是人类必须解开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}makes it imperative that humankind unravel the riddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些宇宙定时炸弹成因之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of what makes these stellar time bombs tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What have you got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 这个是超新星载体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right, so this is the supernova vectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星 嗯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Supernova, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揭秘的关键在于详尽分析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The key to unlocking the mystery lies in detailed analysis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星喷射进宇宙的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of what is ejected into the cosmos by a supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴这个没能逃脱我们的眼睛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l'm glad this one did not escape our attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它是个赢家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}'cause it was a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是颗巨大的超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a great supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大自然给了我们这个难题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nature has given us this puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它说我不费吹灰之力搞出这些物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt says, "l make these objects easily"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们作为理论家就必须搞明白它的性质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and we, as theorists, have to figure out how nature does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和所有的犯罪现场一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As with any crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键的线索就在现场的痕迹中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}critical clues are contained in what is left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和枪击一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like a gunshot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死星爆炸的热气体和碎片会推进到宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}hot gases and explosive debris are propelled through space...by these deadly stellar explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像枪击有一个冲击波一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just as these gunshots are driving a shockwave...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以听到冲击波产生的巨大的声响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you could hear this strong noise from the shockwave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上是压缩并加热了物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's actually compressing the matter and heating it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超新星的冲击波同样如此\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A shockwave in a supernova is doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着这些弹片飞速穿过空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As these pieces of shrapnel are hurtling very fast through space...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与周围的物质发生碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they collide with the material around it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种形式就是冲击波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and what forms is a shockwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神奇的恒星爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The fantastic stellar detonation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将大量的超新星证据…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}shoots vast amounts of ballistic supernova evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为残留物的宇宙碎片射入宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}cosmic debris called remnants, into the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管残留物产生于这个冲击波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Though the remnants are produced as this shockwave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路穿行于宇宙间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}keeps on moving out through the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上产生了一个向外冲击的非常美丽的图像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it actually produces this very picturesque image...of the shock moving outward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那颗星掀起的气体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The gases that made up that star...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巨大的速度喷射 达到每秒一万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are ejected at tremendous velocities, 10,000 miles a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 它们打造了一个不断膨胀的外壳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so they create an expanding shell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终会变得非常非常的大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and eventually that can become very, very large.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西将持续数千年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These things go for thousands of years...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至数万年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or even tens of thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们在爆发发生后数万年还能看到它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So sometimes we can see the sight of a supernova explosion...tens of thousands of years after the event has taken place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星碎片在冲击波里的高速碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The high-speed collision of stellar debris in the shockwave...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生了高温以及肉眼可以看到的光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}produces intense heat and light...in wavelengths invisible to the human eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括电波 红外线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They include radio, infrared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的X射线和伽玛射线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the way to X-rays and gamma rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文学家幸亏有了成熟的空间仪器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fortunately for astronomers...sophisticated space-based instruments...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如哈勃太空望远镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like Hubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史匹哲太空望远镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Spitzer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及钱德拉X射线望远镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the Chandra X-ray Telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助这些宇宙侦探来捕捉到它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can help the cosmic detectives see them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上你可以用上的方方面面的每一件仪器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, basically, every instrument in everyway you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能给你带来所发生情况的各方面的视角\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}gives you a somewhat different perspective on what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你将它们整合在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So then you try to put all that together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不失为明智之举\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as an intellectual enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像指纹一样每个超新星都有其独特的式样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like a fingerprint, each supernova has a unique pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以以几种不同的方式进行分析\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they can be analyzed in several different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以做的一件事就是测量超新星的亮度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One thing we can do is measure how bright the supernova is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们所说的光变曲线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's what we call the light curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以做的另一件事就是可以测量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The other thing that we can measure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有用的东西我们叫做光谱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that is really helpful is what we call the spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从望远镜里获得超新星的光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We take the light from a supernova at a telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用棱镜或光栅将其延展成小小的彩虹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}spread it out into a little rainbow, using a prism or a grating...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后测量在各个颜色或波长上有多少光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then measure how much light there is...at each color orwavelength.
