Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如超新星的化学成分 温度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like the chemical composition of the supernova, the temperature...
