Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从光变曲线及光谱中收集的星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnformation gleaned from the light curve and spectrum...
