Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过逐个比对数百个超新星爆发的光变曲线和光谱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By comparing the light curves and spectra...from literally hundreds of supernova cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家已经能够将超新星归类成两种主要的类型\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}scientists have been able to classify supernovas into two main types.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,典型的1A超新星释放不出氢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Type1a supernovae release no hydrogen.
