Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其爆发的规模和亮度异常强烈\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The explosions vary greatly in size and luminosity.
