Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家重点放在揭示这个重大问题:\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists focus their efforts on uncovering the mammoth question:
