Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜寻着穷凶极恶的超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}looking for deadly supernovas.
