Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 被人类亲眼目睹的第一颗超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln fact, the first supernova everwitnessed by man...
