Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用中国的皇家记录\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Using the royal Chinese records...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的恒星调查员最近发现了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}stellar investigators today have recently found...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗古代超新星的残骸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the remnant of this ancient supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被确认为RCW86\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is identified as RCW86...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人马座里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and is in the constellation Centaurus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的两颗亮星分别叫半人马α和β\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}near two bright stars known as Alpha and Beta Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中国人发现后1400年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}1,400 years after the Chinese discovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个欧洲观察者目睹了一颗超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the first European observer witnessed a supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1572年11月11日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On November11, 1572...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,26岁的丹麦天文学家第谷·布拉赫散步时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}26-year-old Danish astronomer Tycho Brahe was taking a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在北方天空看到了一幕惊人的星象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when he witnessed a shocking stellar phenomenon...in the northern sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧贴着仙女座最亮的星蚀刻出的"W"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt was right next to the "W"...etched by the brightest stars in the constellation Cassiopeia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使他看到了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even though he saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使他已是当时杰出的天文学家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and even though he was the leading astronomer of his age...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他依然不相信自己所看到的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he did not believe the sense of his own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第谷不同寻常的一瞥过去几年后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A few years after Tycho's remarkable sighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他以前的学生 约翰内斯·开普勒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}his former pupil, Johannes Kepler...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实现了他对一颗新星突破性的观察\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}made his own groundbreaking observation of a new star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他围绕着它一颗星一颗星地测量距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He measured from star to star around it, the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在可以用来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And we can use that now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准确地重建它爆发当时的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to recreate exactly the position of where it exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在当代观察员仔细观察开普勒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When contemporary investigators...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1604年的残留物时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}took a closer look at Kepler's 1604 remnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们发现其中很奇怪的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they found something very strange about it.
