Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表明有两颗恒星以某种方式纠集在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}indicated that there were two stars that somehow conjoined...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生了巨大的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to produce a gigantic explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这对伴侣是如何引发这星灾的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So how did this companion cause the stellar catastrophe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多恒星都是双星系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Many stars are in binary systems...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以它们都有一个伙伴围绕着它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so they have a partner that is orbiting around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为结果是一颗恒星将质量转移给另一颗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And we think what happens is that one star puts mass onto the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专家们已经发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Experts have since found...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种结伴或双星的场景是所谓的1A超新星的特征\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the companion, or binary, scenario is the hallmark...of what is called a Type 1a supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I型超新星 我们认为是白矮星的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Type l supernovae, we think, are the explosion of white dwarfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳这样的恒星会变成不大的致密的金块\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So a star like the Sun will produce a little, dense nugget...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如地球一般大小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about the size of the Earth.
