Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做白矮星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}called a white dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳的尸体将成为碳氧白矮星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ashes of the Sun will be a carbon-and-oxygen white dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任其自生自灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Left to its own devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后将永远冷却\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that will just last forever and cool off.
