Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会导致灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it can lead to catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一颗恒星将质量转移给白矮星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One star puts mass onto that white dwarf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将质量增加到了变得不稳定的地步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}pushes its mass up to the point where it becomes unstable...
