Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And very, very rapidly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗恒星就会从乏善可陈的白矮星变成\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the star goes from being a kind of boring white dwarf...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一颗极其暴戾 明亮的超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to being a tremendously violent and brilliant supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 为何某些白矮星会悲惨地爆发呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But why do some white dwarfs catastrophically explode?
